description:
Sam and Colby perform a ritual with Valkyrae and Fuslie in the most haunted small town in America. Mineral Springs Hotel, specifically the pool, is the most haunted location in the city, let's see if it lives up to it's name.

Check us out in your local Zumiez!!! or here: https://www.zumiez.com/xplr-by-sam-and-colby

Subscribe to our Reacts Channel: youtube.com/c/SamandColbyReacts

Make sure to Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/c/samandcolby/?sub_confirmation=1

Join XPLR CLUB: http://xplrclub.com/
What's XPLR CLUB? it's sam and colby's very own social media platform! You'll get everything from extra haunted investigations to podcasts to vlog adventures to giveaways where you could win the chance to be in their next video! watch the video here: http://xplrclub.com/

Huge thanks to Mineral Springs Hotel for having us out!
